{"tid":1550561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"每次集會前都應該唱我願榮光歸香港","createTime":"2019-09-07T16:35:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T16:12:07.000Z","uid":156865,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ace16a1ef543ccff16cedd2d18450cd465c00bf7","tid":1550561,"uid":156865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:35:28.000Z","msg":"我明大家覺得呢首歌未必可以代表咩<br />\n但起碼佢每一句歌詞都代表到呢場運動<br />\n我自己每次聽都好有感觸<br />\n團結每個香港人係重要嘅事 當每次開始前都唱呢首歌 自然會得到社會甚至係國際嘅更大關注<br />\n亦可以作為一個先例 喺往後好多年嘅運動中去團結港人<br />\n記住不割蓆不篤灰嘅精神<br />\n喺呢場運動中 呢個精神先係最可貴 值得我地去將佢傳承去未來每一個運動<br />\n<br />\n我知我講到1999 希望有人明<br />\n歡迎各位指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f291ec844e35da71923c7a6fb36187a59fdc5364","tid":1550561,"uid":9448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:35:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d8c2dac2df11fb99eaa7d6c87df4b1ba81a4501","tid":1550561,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:36:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b36eee4f876ead40a3cae8994ea1980d3c4d2301","tid":1550561,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:36:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"77e32f57c7ce74a66b78d78891479ac93a5e7d69","tid":1550561,"uid":156865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:38:53.000Z","msg":"自推 希望比更多人睇到"},{"pid":"d8bf0ef27ad489e80b0b8c77c870077ec5caf453","tid":1550561,"uid":266617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:39:54.000Z","msg":"推到所有香港人識唱"},{"pid":"c56c97b5f98bb9a827febf5176243ae5a4ae8f3b","tid":1550561,"uid":199712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:41:15.000Z","msg":"聽日唱咗美國國歌先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n始終係去美領，唱完美國國歌先唱香港國歌<br />\n咁樣會尊重啲"},{"pid":"27322c69ec20ff36c2c240f5cc0284d1d7af0671","tid":1550561,"uid":156865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8bf0ef27ad489e80b0b8c77c870077ec5caf453","tid":1550561,"uid":266617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:39:54.000Z","msg":"推到所有香港人識唱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:41:37.000Z","msg":"其實最好背咗歌詞佢 個畫面會好壯麗"},{"pid":"b1f4cde239b05067aed798749c5ffdb1f6a9b8f0","tid":1550561,"uid":156865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c56c97b5f98bb9a827febf5176243ae5a4ae8f3b","tid":1550561,"uid":199712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:41:15.000Z","msg":"聽日唱咗美國國歌先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n始終係去美領，唱完美國國歌先唱香港國歌<br />\n咁樣會尊重啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:43:26.000Z","msg":"咁當然冇問題 最緊要係真香港人精神要傳承落去<br />\n團結一致 對抗不公"},{"pid":"dfb64d35ef21ae8b965e01bfe0bb9f64fc0276a7","tid":1550561,"uid":239496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:44:37.000Z","msg":"有冇人識佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rgqT14t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrgqT14t.jpg&h=86419bb9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d271d4c1b707953b226652fba22c8b3d3879b43","tid":1550561,"uid":124180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy"